A man who evidently wanted to get drunk - or already was - drove his car into the front a liquor store in Houston, Texas, so he could steal booze.

The suspect used his four-door car to smash through the front of the Louetta Discount Liquor store around 5am on Saturday.

Officers from the Harris County Sheriff's Office are on the lookout for the man.

